    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/541cfd05aef520dd9e5b4213174d609b.poster.avif?t=1762158772\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/541cfd05aef520dd9e5b4213174d609b.webm?t=1762158772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/541cfd05aef520dd9e5b4213174d609b.mp4?t=1762158772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Duriano: Epic Durian Heros</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A thrilling 3D top-down action roguelite adventure into the world of Norse Mythology, where you become the unlikely hero… a <strong>Durian</strong>! Prepare yourself, grab mighty weapons, unleash divine powers, and vanquish the Gods of Asgard! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/3a445a1b90851671c4e43bc315d20fe2.avif?t=1762158772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras_big/3a445a1b90851671c4e43bc315d20fe2.avif?t=1762158772 width=800 height=432 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Durian Hero Variants</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Durian Heroes… Unleash the Power of Gods!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your Durian hero! Each variant embodies unique powers and abilities inspired by Norse Gods and mythical creatures. Tailor your playstyle, harness their divine essence, and embark on your epic quest! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/9140d81f2bcc329dc5e5271a3d2057d3.poster.avif?t=1762158772\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/9140d81f2bcc329dc5e5271a3d2057d3.webm?t=1762158772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/9140d81f2bcc329dc5e5271a3d2057d3.mp4?t=1762158772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fate's Favors &amp; God Path</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose Your God Path… Unlock Ultimate Power!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Empower your Durian Hero with &quot;Fate's Favors,&quot; granting powerful buffs and unique abilities! Select a &quot;God Path&quot; to unlock spectacular combat skills and customize your hero to perfection!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/269c8903eb4a5f31d20a3780cdf8e40e.poster.avif?t=1762158772\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/269c8903eb4a5f31d20a3780cdf8e40e.webm?t=1762158772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/269c8903eb4a5f31d20a3780cdf8e40e.mp4?t=1762158772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mythic Weapons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mythical Arsenal Awaits… Unleash Devastating Power!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and collect hundreds of &quot;Mythic Weapons,&quot; each with unique attributes and game-changing effects! Fuse weapon power with your Durian Hero's abilities to create unstoppable combos! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/280f75b4802ba5b31c7f2116d9472f00.avif?t=1762158772\" width=616 height=758 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Synergistic Combos</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Master Combos… Unleash Limitless Potential!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment and combine everything! Durian Hero variants, Fate's Favors, and weapons – discover synergistic combos to unleash devastating power and obliterate your foes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/70f61726332b93a8525158047ec05945.avif?t=1762158772\" width=616 height=758 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Adaptive Strategy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Every Run Unique… Conquer the Ever-Changing Challenge!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill of Roguelite gameplay where every run is different! New environments, new enemies, new challenges await! Adapt your strategy on the fly and overcome every obstacle!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/a5d60c6950321d21063bdccdefd6320f.poster.avif?t=1762158772\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/a5d60c6950321d21063bdccdefd6320f.webm?t=1762158772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/a5d60c6950321d21063bdccdefd6320f.mp4?t=1762158772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Progression and Customization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Upgrades… Evolve Your Hero to Godlike Status!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep playing to unlock new Durian Hero variants, Fate's Favors, and weapons! Collect and upgrade your arsenal to make your hero stronger and face even greater challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/82a5fe59aee9b1b396a5bf4fc0118888.avif?t=1762158772\" width=616 height=360 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Prepare for Battle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get Ready to Rumble! Dive into the mystical Norse realms, embark on an epic action-packed adventure, master devastating combos, and lead your Durian Hero to victory over the Gods of Asgard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to become the ultimate Durian Hero? Join the fight in Duriano and etch your legend into the annals of Asgardian history!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/b8328dfa93b4134b84d67035e489fa55.poster.avif?t=1762158772\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/b8328dfa93b4134b84d67035e489fa55.webm?t=1762158772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048930/extras/b8328dfa93b4134b84d67035e489fa55.mp4?t=1762158772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
